<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />When you get used to the cold,<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />walks in the snow are pretty chill!<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Check it out, <tag a="110" b="3" />!<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />When we stand out in the snow, it's
kind of like we're in a snow globe!<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well<tag a="110" b="0" />we're not underwater, and the
snow is real, but you get the idea.<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="1" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Don't you think <tag a="110" b="9" /> is
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />totally beautiful when it snows?<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="1" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You ever heard of the Snowsquatch?<delay frames="40" />
They say it doesn't exist. But I heard
the same thing about UFOs too<tag a="110" b="0" /><setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="1" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hey again, <tag a="110" b="3" />!<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Snow shines kind of like diamonds,<delay20 />
right? <anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />Sometimes I get hypnotized!<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="1" cancelOption="1" /></message>
</msbt>